_:N4dce5b014de044ca89982b13a3da0794 <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pKsxtzbSqBU\" class=\"govuk-link\">Working for Gov Facility Services Ltd - What’s it like on the inside?</a></p>\n\n<p>GFSL supply facilities management services to 50 prisons over the south of the UK. With a staff count of over 1400 we strive to be the facilities management employer of choice.</p>\n\n<p>Successful candidates will be offered a competitive salary along with a generous 25 days holiday + bank holidays, a good pension scheme and other benefits such as an annual performance award, days away from work to support charities, access to the government’s discount portal on high street retailers, holidays, insurance, and much more.</p>\n\n<p>We advertise our vacancies across numerous platforms suitable to the role and location. \nOur vacancies are also listed on our <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://findajob.dwp.gov.uk/search?q=Gov+Facility+Services\" class=\"govuk-link\">jobs page</a>, on <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/gov-facility-services-lts/\" class=\"govuk-link\">Linkedin</a> and on local jobs boards.</p>\n\n<p>If you’re interested in working for GFSL or have any questions about recruitment, contact us at: <a href=\"mailto:gfsl_recruitment@govfsl.com\" class=\"govuk-link\">gfsl_recruitment@govfsl.com</a></p>\n\n<p>Note: The video was filmed in late 2020 with full Covid-secure safety measures in place. We maintain Covid-secure measures on all our establishment sites.</p>\n</div>" .
